title: Boo Chonkers
description: Meet Boo Chonkers - your new favorite chubby ghost! This star-shaped ghost, with its big expressive eyes and welcoming arms, is set to bring joy to your Halloween decorations. This fun and adorable figure is designed for quick and easy printing with simple support removal. Remember not to place it near an open flame. Show off your creation by sharing a photo, sending a note, or even treating the artist to a pizza slice.

title: Pumpkin and Candy Corn Ornaments
description: Unleash your creativity with these Pumpkin and Candy Corn Ornaments! The unique design allows you to pause the printing process to add multiple colors, creating a realistic candy corn effect. For an added touch of authenticity, the pumpkin's body and stem are printed separately and then assembled. Perfect for adding a touch of fall warmth to any space!

title: Moving Single Eye
description: Introducing the Moving Single Eye - a compact box designed to hold two servos with a single eye. Initially created for a Halloween trunk-or-treat display, this box can be assembled quickly and easily, making it perfect for large-scale displays. The eyes are a breeze to build, making use of dry-brush painting and 12mm cabochons. This model is slightly fragile but boasts a longer life and quicker build time. Please note this model comes with detailed instructions and a supply list. Get ready to create a mesmerizing wall of eyes this Halloween!

title: Thanksgiving SVG/STL's
description: Enhance your 3D projects with these Thanksgiving-themed SVG's and STL's! Perfect for adding a festive touch to your creations. Easy to use and perfect for personal or professional projects.

title: Ghost badge/fridge magnet.
description: This adorable ghost is not only a decorative piece, but it can also be a badge or a fridge magnet. Its charming google eyes are securely fastened with superglue, and a hot glue gun is used to attach a safety pin or a magnet at the back. Perfect to add a touch of cuteness to your outfit or kitchen.

title: Halloween bat badge/fridge magnet
description: Introducing our adorable Halloween bat, perfect for a badge or a fridge magnet. This charming little creature will definitely add a touch of cuteness to your Halloween decor. Simply use a bit of superglue to attach googly eyes and a hot glue gun for the safety pin or fridge magnet. It's a fun and easy DIY project!

title: Grave Stite
description: Unearth a sense of the macabre and history with our 3D printed Grave Site model. Perfect for those looking to add a touch of the eerie to their model collection or tabletop game. The level of detail and realism in this model will surely captivate and intrigue anyone who sees it.

title: Cave Eyes!
description: Experience the thrill of being watched in the dark with 'Cave Eyes!' This 3D model provides a casing for a circuit board and LED holders designed by Cowlacious Designs. The circuit board, available at Cowlacious.com, generates an enchanting blinking eye effect for up to 16 pairs of LED eyes, making any space feel alive and eerie. The model includes a front and back piece for the eye holders which can be easily glued together. The set also includes a detailed instruction manual for connecting the LEDs and creating the wiring harness with ethernet cables. Perfect for anyone who enjoys a bit of soldering and DIY fun!

title: Skull Candle Holder
description: Illuminate your surroundings with a spooky edge using this Skull Candle Holder. Perfect for creating a chilling ambience, just place a candle in the middle and let it cast an eerie glow.

title: Tomb Stones
description: Discover the intriguing allure of our Tomb Stones 3D model. This collection's realism and attention to detail make it a captivating addition to any Halloween or horror-inspired setting. Whether you're creating a spooky tabletop game or setting up a haunted house, these tombstones will add the perfect chilling touch.

title: Ragno per Halloween
description: This Halloween Spider is a must-have for your spooky decorations! Crafted meticulously, this model is designed to be 3D printed at a layer height of 0.2, but can also be printed at 0.26 to conserve filament. Despite the reduced filament usage, the model retains its stunning detail and durability. With a filling of 5% and a medium-fast speed, this spider will be ready to spook in no time!

title: Ozzy Statue
description: Celebrate the life and legacy of the legendary Ozzy with this finely crafted 3D printed statue. A perfect tribute to a music icon, this piece is sure to add a touch of rock history to any collection.

title: Armenian Khachkar Stone
description: This 3D model captures the intricate beauty of the Armenian Khachkar Stone, a symbol of Armenia's rich cultural and religious heritage. Each Khachkar is a unique work of art, carved with a central cross and a symphony of other motifs. This model is more than just a historical representation; it's a visual prayer, a chronicle of history, and a testament to a nation's identity. Crafted from local volcanic tuff, it's a durable piece that withstands the test of time. Bring home this unique piece of history and let it tell its story.

title: 6-5th century BCE silver coin from the Greek city of Cyrene : Silphium and Magas
description: Get transported back to the Greek city of Cyrene with this meticulously crafted 3D model of a 6-5th century BCE silver coin. Featuring the enigmatic Silphium plant and the legendary King Magas, this model offers a unique glimpse into ancient history and Greek mythology. Perfect for enthusiasts, collectors, and educators alike.

title: Magen David Shield, Star of David
description: Experience the beauty and significance of the Magen David Shield, also known as the Star of David. This 3D model showcases precise detailing, perfect for those who appreciate Jewish culture or historical artifacts.

title: Apollo 11 moon landing lithophane diogram
description: Experience history in an entirely new dimension with this meticulously crafted 3D model depicting the epoch-making Apollo 11 moon landing. This lithophane diorama brings to life the most exciting moment of the Apollo 11 mission, as seen on television. Created for the best quality with a 1.12 layer height, it also offers a standard quality option with a 1.16 layer height. The model requires 5 - 10 percent infill and supports can be used but are not necessary. Whether for your personal collection or a thoughtful gift, this model allows you to hold a piece of history in your hands. Feel free to reach out with any questions or share your finished model in the comments.

title: Ives Church = logo
description: Immerse yourself in the spirit of faith and devotion with this 3D model of the Ives Church evangelical logo. Crafted with precision to represent the essence of sanctity, it's a perfect addition to any religious or historical collection. Layered at 0.20mm with a fill of 15%, it manifests a blend of durability and aesthetic appeal. Rendered in Generic ABS filament, the top surface is fashioned in a unique Hilbert Curve, adding an intriguing dimension to the piece.

title: Book corners based on Codex Gigas
description: Experience the joy of assembling this print model inspired by the Codex Gigas. Designed for a smooth printing process without the need for support, the pieces can be easily glued together after cutting. The result? A unique book corner that adds a touch of historical charm to your reading experience.

title: Soviet AA / DShK aiming device /colimator. 1:1 replica
description: Dive into the pages of history with this detailed 1:1 replica of a Soviet AA / DShK aiming device. Crafted with precision and authenticity, this model brings the past to life in your hands. Perfect for military memorabilia collectors, historical reenactments, and education. For best results, print at a resolution of 0.1-0.2 mm. Note: Some assembly is required.

title: PPSh-41 prop 1:1 replica
description: Get your hands on this immaculate, 1:1 replica of the iconic PPSH-41! Crafted with meticulous details, this model is perfect for prop creation and replicas. Inspired by an original PPSH-41, this 3D printable version brings history to life. Ideal for enthusiasts and collectors alike!

title: Himeji Castle - Japan
description: Feast your eyes on the stunning Himeji Castle, the largest and most visited castle in Japan, and a UNESCO World Heritage Site. This 3D model is a masterpiece created by Zuknaini 'Izu' Mohd Sabri, well known as @izuka.arts. Resembling a white heron in flight, the castle's model is a perfect example of classic Japanese architecture. Originating from the 14th century, the castle has survived World War II bombings and many natural disasters. This model is a tribute from MiniWorld 3D to the people of Japan. With 83 rooms and advanced defensive systems, it's a tangible piece of history right on your desk. Note: Selling of model or prints without license is prohibited. Enjoy 3D printing and spread culture and education!

title: SANTA MARIA FLAG SHIP: SCALE MODEL KIT
description: Experience the joy of assembling your very own Santa Maria Flag Ship with this scale model kit! Comprised of 72 distinct pieces, this kit challenges your crafting skills and rewards you with a beautiful model ship. Detailed instructions with photos are included to guide you through the process. The kit allows for customization - you can print the sails or craft them out of real cloth, and the level of detail you add is entirely up to you! The model is designed for 3D printing with wood PLA, with suggested settings provided for different parts. The final product is a testament to your efforts and a stunning model ship to showcase.

title: Great Sphinx of Giza - Egypt
description: Experience the grandeur of one of the world's most famous landmarks, The Great Sphinx of Giza, with this 3D model meticulously handcrafted by @motherofprinters. This model pays tribute to the oldest known monumental sculpture in Egypt, believed to have been built during the reign of the Pharaoh Khafre around 4,500 years ago! Carved from solid limestone bedrock, the Sphinx is a mythical creature with the body of a lion and the head of a human. This model is a precise representation of the original, measuring 73 m long, 20 m high, and 19 m wide at its rear haunches. Printed in Fillamentum Mukha and Woodfill PLA by Colorfabb, this model is a perfect addition to your collection. Join our Printables.com Club for access to other amazing 3D printable models!

title: Ishtar Gate - Babylon (Iraq)
description: Step into the ancient city of Babylon with our intricate 3D model of the Ishtar Gate. This model, designed by renowned artist Zuknaini 'Izu' Mohd Sabri, features the entire double gate as it originally stood, complete with its vibrant colors and detailed reliefs. It's a nod to history, and a tribute to the people of Iraq. Crafted with passion, this model is a testament to the beauty of ancient architecture and the power of 3D printing technology. Join our club at Printables.com and bring a piece of history to your home.
